{"id":"290455119_Recent_developments_of_matrix_versions_of_the_arithmetic-geometric_mean_inequality","abstract":"The main aim of this survey article is to present recent develop- ments of matrix versions of the arithmetic-geometric mean inequality. Among others, we show improvements and generalizations of the arithmetic-geometric mean inequality for unitarily invariant norms via the Hadamard product, and for singular values via the operator monotone functions.","authors":["Jun Ichi Fujii","Masatoshi Fujii","Yuki Seo","Zuo Hongliang"],"meta":["February 2016Annals of Functional Analysis 7(1):102-117","DOI:10.1215/20088752-3429400"],"references":["251402491_Some_inequalities_for_unitarily_invariant_norms_of_matrices","273507228_Zhan's_inequality_on_A-G_mean_inequalities","266916457_Some_results_on_Kwong_functions_and_related_inequalities","257882650_On_singular_value_inequalities_for_matrix_means","247047254_On_the_Singular_Values_of_a_Product_of_Operators","246870086_More_Matrix_Forms_of_the_Arithmetic-Geometric_Mean_Inequality","246462914_Inequalities_for_Unitarily_Invariant_Norms","240335174_The_Singular_Values_of_a_Hadamard_Product_A_Basic_Inequality_Lin_Multilin_Alg_21_345-365","238850709_More_results_on_singular_value_inequalities_of_matrices","235258334_Further_refinements_of_the_Heinz_inequality","232819721_Some_research_problems_on_the_Hadamard_product_and_singular_values_of_matrices","225648445_On_the_Convexity_of_the_Heinz_Means","222472438_An_arithmetic-geometric-harmonic_mean_inequality_involving_Hadamard_products","222391088_Some_results_on_matrix_monotone_functions","222219692_Notes_on_matrix_arithmetic-geometric_mean_inequalities","2130921_A_Singular_Value_Inequality_for_Heinz_Means"]}